tell us about that.

53:46.531 --> 53:49.564
You lied to us. Well,
you didn't lie, but you...

53:49.566 --> 53:51.635
didn't tell us
the whole story here.

53:54.905 --> 53:58.475
Fantastic. It's unbelievable
that you could tell me that.

53:59.477 --> 54:01.910
Maggie, do you mind if I...

54:01.912 --> 54:04.015
...just had
a moment with Paul?

54:06.050 --> 54:08.419
