56:44.874 --> 56:47.975
but I just want to encourage you
to be honest with yourself.

56:47.977 --> 56:49.645
You never had a husband, right?

56:49.647 --> 56:51.946
Yeah. Don't remind me.

56:51.948 --> 56:53.084
So why <i>are</i> you here?

56:55.053 --> 56:58.654
